{{作品名稱|name=''Primary Colors''|hk=這個總統真太濫|tw=風起雲湧|equiv-cn=tw}}是一套1998年的美國政治電影，由[[米克·尼高斯|米克·尼高斯]]執導。內容改編自{{link-en|影射小說|Roman à clef}}《''{{link-en|Primary Colors (novel)|Primary Colors (novel)|Primary Colors: A Novel of Politics}}''》，影射{{link-en|1992年比爾·克林頓總統競選|Bill Clinton presidential campaign, 1992}}，最初以匿名出版，但在1996年被披露作者是記者{{link-en|Joe Klein|Joe Klein}}，他為《[[新聞週刊|新聞週刊]]》報道克林頓的競選。<ref name="what the">{{Cite web |url = http://articles.latimes.com/1998/mar/15/entertainment/ca-28949 |title = What the Movie Gets --and What It Doesn't |author = David Lauter |date = 1998-03-15 |publisher = The Los Angeles Times |language = en |accessdate = 2017-02-21 |archive-date = 2012-03-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120309140216/http://articles.latimes.com/1998/mar/15/entertainment/ca-28949 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://articles.latimes.com/1998/mar/02/entertainment/ca-24508 |title = Just What He Didn't Need Right Now |author = Faye Fiore |date = 1998-03-02 |publisher = The Los Angeles Times |language = en |accessdate = 2017-02-21 |archive-date = 2012-11-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121104155107/http://articles.latimes.com/1998/mar/02/entertainment/ca-24508 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.nytimes.com/1996/07/18/us/columnist-s-mea-culpa-i-m-anonymous.html |title = Columnist's Mea Culpa: I'm Anonymous |author = Doreen Carvajal |date = 1996-07-18 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en}}</ref>主演有[[尊·特拉華特|尊·特拉華特]]、[[愛瑪·湯遜|愛瑪·湯遜]]、[[比利·卜·科頓|比利·卜·科頓]]、[[嘉菲·比絲|嘉菲·比絲]]、{{link-en|毛拉·蒂爾尼|Maura Tierney}}、{{link-en|Larry Hagman|Larry Hagman}}和[[艾哲倫·雷斯特|艾哲倫·雷斯特]]。

比絲憑她的演出被提名[[奧斯卡最佳女配角|奧斯卡最佳女配角]]，而伊萊恩·梅則被提名[[奧斯卡最佳改編劇本|奧斯卡最佳改編劇本]]

